extendedInfo.description: Pregnancy Calculator estimates due date by last menstrual period. You can add very cute Widget to track your weeks and days progress. Take a picture of yourself each week.Calculator Features:- Days, weeks and months to go and which have passed- Estimated day of the week- Estimated season and zodiac- Current trimester- Historical events of estimated due date- Get daily notification- Share the date by Facebook or by EmailPhotos Features:- Take and view a picture of yourself each week- Share you picturesWidget Features:- Very cute widget that tracks your weeks and days daily progress===============If you have any problems, improvements or suggestions please contact me by email: sromku@gmail.com ===============We have found a new way to generate some money from this free app. using this new search tool, we can keep creating apps and give them to you completely free forever! reviews.title: Good for what it does.
reviews.comment: It can tell you the information about where you are at in your pregnancy but nothing more. Also in app due date calculator only uses 28 day cycle. The widget is cute but im not a flower girl and would have preferred something different. This app has potential to be great but needs a few changes. Calculating due date by ovulation date would be a good add on or being allowed to change cycle length. I hope to see better improvements and less notifications cause if I want notifications id select a different app
reviews.author: Samantha Matthews

reviews.title: Daily notifications a bit irritating but otherwise ok
reviews.comment: The daily notifications are irritating, perhaps you could add an option to customise to weekly or monthly? Love the widget, very cute but would like a bit more in the way of development info etc. Love the weekly photos bit, I did this with my son & it\'s nice to see the growing bump although it would be good to be able to add photos from previous weeks :-)
